l Anghelinei ([[Gala\u021bi]])\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date= 14 June 2003\n|time= 18:00 [[Eastern European Summer Time|EEST]] ([[UTC+03:00|UTC+3]])\n|team1= [[ASC O\u021belul Gala\u021bi|O\u021belul Gala\u021bi]]\n|score= 2\u20131\n|report= https://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_a/2002_03/play_off.shtml\n|team2= '''[[FC Bihor Oradea|FC Oradea]]'''\n|goals1= [[Cornel Cornea|Cornea]] {{goal|28}}<br>[[Mihai Guri\u021b\u0103|Guri\u021b\u0103]] {{goal|67}}\n|goals2= [[Bogdan Vr\u0103jitoarea|Vr\u0103jitoarea]] {{goal|45|pen.}}\n|stadium= [[Stadionul O\u021belul|O\u021belul]]\n|location= [[Gala\u021bi]]\n|attendance= 7,000\n|referee= Marian Salomir ([[Cluj-Napoca]])\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date= 18 June 2003\n|time= 17:30 [[Eastern European Summer Time|EEST]] ([[UTC+03:00|UTC+3]])\n|team1= '''[[FC Gloria Buz\u0103u|Gloria Buz\u0103u]]'''\n|score= 1\u20133\n|report= https://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_a/2002_03/play_off.shtml\n|team2= [[FC Politehnica Timi\u0219oara|Poli AEK Timi\u0219oara]]\n|goals1= [[Dumitru Gheorghe (footballer)|D.Gheorghe]] {{goal|90+3}}\n|goals2= [[Florin Constantinovici|Constantinovici]] {{goal|13}}<br>[[Romulus Buia|Buia]] {{goal|48}}<br>[[C\u0103lin Zanc|Zanc]] {{goal|69}}\n|stadium= [[Stadionul Municipal (Buz\u0103u)|Municipal]]\n|location= [[Buz\u0103u]]\n|attendance= 15,000\n|referee= Sorin Corpodean ([[Alba Iulia]])\n}}\n{{footballbox collapsible\n|date= 18 June 2003\n|time= 17:30 [[Eastern European Summer Time|EEST]] ([[UTC+03:00|UTC+3]])\n|team1= [[FC Bihor Oradea|FC Oradea]]\n|score= 3\u20131 {{aet}}\n|report= https://www.romaniansoccer.ro/divizia_a/2002_03/play_off.shtml\n|team2= '''[[ASC O\u021belul Gala\u021bi|O\u021belul Gala\u021bi]]'''\n|goals1= [[Bogdan Vr\u0103jitoarea|Vr\u0103jitoarea]] {{goal|70||81}} {{golden goal|91}}\n|goals2= [[Viorel T\u0103nase|V.T\u0103nase]] {{goal|28}}\n|stadium= [[Stadionul Iuliu Bodola|Municipal]]\n|location= [[Oradea]]\n|attendance= 20,000\n|referee= [[Cristian Balaj]] ([[Baia Mare]]